channel.title: [SRL][RS2] Juniors Draynor Yew Cutter V1.4[RS2][SRL]
channel.description:
[b][size=10pt][size=10pt]JUNIORS DRAYNOR YEW CUTTER V1.4[/size][/size][/b]
[size=20pt]WARING[/size]: This script is OUTDATED! It probably wont run with the new version of SRL. Use it at your own risk, and dont expect it to be perfect, it was one of the [b]first[/b] scripts I made.
Thanks [b]chris[/b] for hacking into my account, changing the password, and trying to put a PIN on my bank. I have the account back and I will just like to say thanks for the [u]770 free yew logs[/u] you cut for me. And thanks again for the [u]3 woodcutting levels![/u]
[b]Version 1.5 will not be out until 1 to 2 weeks.[/b]
Yo guys whats up, its Junior as you already know.
This is the latest creation I have been working on for quite a while now. I have been testing it for a while now and fixing little things here and there, but now I need more people to test, post progress reports, and notify me of any errors.
[u][b]PROGRESS[/b][/u] [scar] <~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~ /\ jR SCARWriters /\ One Tree Draynor YEW CUTTER <~-~------------------------------------------------------------------ /\ Worked for 29 Minutes and 0 Seconds /\ Chopped about 54 Logs /\ Completed 2 Bank Trips /\ Gained about 17280 XP /\ Avoided a total of 0 Ents! <~-~------------------------------------------------------------------ /\ Current RoadColor: 6908529 /\ Current BankSymbol Color: 6478070 /\ Current Quest Symbol Color: 15956845 <~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~-~
/~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\ | SRL Randoms Report | | www.villu-reborn.com | |~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~| | Talking Random[s] : 1 | | Rick[s] Solved : 1 | \~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~/
[/scar]
[b][u]WARNING:[/u][/b] READ ALL RULES BEFORE STARTING SCRIPT. AND I AM NOT RESPONSIBLE FOR ANY BANNED ACCOUNT.
But dont worry, during this whole script I have only received 1 mysterious old man random, so I think thats pretty good.
This script will start in Draynor bank, walk to the yew tree, chop a full load, then hopefully walk back to the bank, deposite, and then repeat the process again.
AND, the purpose of the BLUE WATER STAFF is to detect if the player is just standing there or cutting down the tree. When the staff is gone it tells the script to do certain procedures, and when it is visible it tells the script to do other procedures.
One last thing. I reccomend you watch the script as it is the first release, just setting the script and walking off does not help me or you.
[size=10pt][b][u]Bugs[/u]:[/b][/size] - Working on fixing bank walking procedure, the road color changes sometimes on the way to Yew tree. (Made temporary procedure, adding a very good one soon by Tarajunky.) [b]^FIXED - added tarajunky's auto color procedure[/b] - Fixing ent finding, not exactly working. [b]^FIXED - Used SRL ent procedure. --- Still having problems with this, sorry guys.[/b] - Bank walking sucked. [b]^Made a new bank walking procedure, works alot better! --- Still having problems with this too.[/b]
[size=10pt][b][u]Version History[/u]:[/b][/size] - [u][b]Verison 1.0 -[/b][/u] First Release - [u][b]Version 1.1 -[/b][/u] Temporary road color changing procedure, Making a better one soon. - [u][b]Version 1.2 -[/b][/u] Received a auto road color procedure from Tarajunky, added that in(Works like a charm!). Made a procedure that detects if you went up any levels, used SRL ent procedure. - [u][b]Version 1.3 -[/b][/u] Fixed Runtime error caused by mislabelled arrays, new progress report, added "FindRandoms;" procedure more often in my "ChopYews;" procedure. - [u][b]Version 1.4 -[/b][/u] Newer progress report, [u]better bank walking[/u], edited SRL ent procedure, added more new auto colors, removed unecessary procedures.
Enjoy. :D ~jR
